1
00:00:08,625 --> 00:00:09,916
[SAKURA] Last time on
Zombie Land Saga, you met me,

2
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,458
Sakura Minamoto,
a girl full of hopes and dreams!

3
00:00:12,541 --> 00:00:14,000
Then, I got hit
by a truck and died.

4
00:00:14,083 --> 00:00:15,500
Which was sad, but then it was,
like, "Just kidding,

5
00:00:15,583 --> 00:00:16,875
you're still here,
good morning!"

6
00:00:16,958 --> 00:00:18,208
Crazy, right?

7
00:00:18,291 --> 00:00:19,750
Then, I ran away
and got shot by a policeman,

8
00:00:19,833 --> 00:00:21,375
and now this weird guy says
I have to become an idol

9
00:00:21,458 --> 00:00:22,625
and save Saga.

10
00:00:22,708 --> 00:00:24,708
Oh yeah, did I mention
I'm a zombie now?

11
00:00:24,791 --> 00:00:27,875
After all that, I feel like
pretty much anything can happen!

12
00:00:32,708 --> 00:00:35,375
-[gasps]
-[zombie groaning]

13
00:00:42,041 --> 00:00:43,958
[puffs cigarette]

14
00:00:44,041 --> 00:00:45,875
[whimpering]

15
00:00:45,958 --> 00:00:47,208
[SAKURA]
They really did snap out of it

16
00:00:47,291 --> 00:00:49,125
after last night's show.

17
00:00:49,208 --> 00:00:50,500
[TAE groans]

18
00:00:50,583 --> 00:00:52,916
Well, except for Tae, I guess.

19
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:55,041
[door opens, closes]

20
00:00:58,583 --> 00:01:02,125
Hello there, ladies.
Congrats on your awakening.

21
00:01:04,916 --> 00:01:06,250
[angry exhale]

22
00:01:06,333 --> 00:01:08,958
[whimpers]

23
00:01:09,041 --> 00:01:11,250
I said congratulations!

24
00:01:17,625 --> 00:01:21,625
I am your mysterious, new idol
producer, the Kotaro Tatsumi!

25
00:01:21,708 --> 00:01:23,750
Your job is to become
pop sensations,

26
00:01:23,833 --> 00:01:26,750
and save Saga
from oblivion! Boom!

27
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:30,250
Using all of your
legendary qualities,

28
00:01:30,333 --> 00:01:34,208
we can put this
prefecture on the map!

29
00:01:34,291 --> 00:01:36,208
[KOTARO]
Ahh!

30
00:03:10,875 --> 00:03:12,583
Man, this sucks!

31
00:03:12,666 --> 00:03:14,708
I don't friggin'
get what's goin' on.

32
00:03:14,791 --> 00:03:16,708
Oh? What's stumping you?

33
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:20,250
You're sayin' I died.

34
00:03:20,333 --> 00:03:22,000
So how'm I still movin' around?

35
00:03:22,083 --> 00:03:24,833
Aw, you haven't wrapped
your little brain around it yet?

36
00:03:24,916 --> 00:03:26,375
[angrily growls]

37
00:03:26,458 --> 00:03:29,208
-Think about it carefully, Saki.
-Don't talk like I'm--

38
00:03:29,291 --> 00:03:31,041
You're a zombie now!

39
00:03:31,125 --> 00:03:32,583
You died and then you came back.

40
00:03:32,666 --> 00:03:34,125
What other way
is there to explain it?

41
00:03:34,208 --> 00:03:35,416
You ever seen a living,

42
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:37,416
breathing girl
with a green face?

43
00:03:37,500 --> 00:03:40,333
Once again, all of you girls
are fortunate enough

44
00:03:40,416 --> 00:03:41,750
to have risen from the dead.

45
00:03:41,833 --> 00:03:43,208
But as you may've guessed,

46
00:03:43,291 --> 00:03:45,208
there's no place for zombies
in regular society!

47
00:03:45,291 --> 00:03:47,000
By making you celebrities,

48
00:03:47,083 --> 00:03:50,125
I'm giving you undead outcasts
a purpose and a place to stay,

49
00:03:50,208 --> 00:03:52,000
so be grateful!

50
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:56,000
Anyway, it's time
for a pop quiz.

51
00:03:56,083 --> 00:03:57,625
If you're gonna become
a zombie idol group,

52
00:03:57,708 --> 00:03:59,833
then what's the number one
thing you must do?

53
00:03:59,916 --> 00:04:01,583
-Uh. Sakura!
-Me?

54
00:04:01,666 --> 00:04:03,041
Uh, I dunno.

55
00:04:03,125 --> 00:04:04,541
Like not bite people?

56
00:04:04,625 --> 00:04:07,916
Don't let people know
you're zombies, dumb zombie!

57
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,083
[whimpers]

58
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:12,166
-[zombie screaming]
-[smashing of skulls]

59
00:04:17,833 --> 00:04:19,291
-[clicks keyboard key]
-See?

60
00:04:19,375 --> 00:04:21,083
That's what'll happen to you
girls if people find out.

61
00:04:21,166 --> 00:04:22,500
-[cries quietly]
-[KOTARO] But if you take

62
00:04:22,583 --> 00:04:25,000
certain safety precautions,
you might be okay.

63
00:04:25,083 --> 00:04:27,083
Like referring to yourselves
with numbers

64
00:04:27,166 --> 00:04:28,791
instead of your real names.

65
00:04:28,875 --> 00:04:31,000
[AI] Listen, I get that
we're zombies and all.

66
00:04:31,083 --> 00:04:34,041
But is there a reason
we have to be idols, too?

67
00:04:34,125 --> 00:04:36,083
So Saga can be saved.

68
00:04:36,166 --> 00:04:38,291
[AI] We're gonna do
the local idol thing?

69
00:04:38,375 --> 00:04:39,500
That's stupid!

70
00:04:39,583 --> 00:04:41,291
[KOTARO]
Kinda sounds like you're scared.

71
00:04:41,375 --> 00:04:42,500
[AI scoffs]

72
00:04:42,583 --> 00:04:43,958
[AI]
I just know that it won't work!

73
00:04:44,041 --> 00:04:45,250
I mean, look at us,

74
00:04:45,333 --> 00:04:46,708
we're a bunch of rotting,
dead bodies here!

75
00:04:46,791 --> 00:04:49,166
And besides,
I wasn't even from Saga!

76
00:04:49,250 --> 00:04:50,666
[KOTARO chuckles]

77
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:52,666
-Saga don't sweat the details!
-[AI scoffs]

78
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:55,250
Local slang,
you wouldn't understand.

79
00:04:55,333 --> 00:04:57,333
Hey, I know about Saga!

80
00:04:57,416 --> 00:05:00,458
Well, why don't you tell me what
you know about it then, huh?

81
00:05:00,541 --> 00:05:02,333
It's in... Kyushu!

82
00:05:02,416 --> 00:05:04,291
Good job!

83
00:05:04,375 --> 00:05:06,583
You know basic geography!

84
00:05:06,666 --> 00:05:09,625
Fine. Then, what do you know
about it, Mr. Expert?

85
00:05:09,708 --> 00:05:13,583
I know Saga from top to bottom.
Everything there is to know.

86
00:05:13,666 --> 00:05:15,250
What's the population?

87
00:05:15,333 --> 00:05:16,375
That's easy!

88
00:05:16,458 --> 00:05:18,250
I'll tell you to the decimal!

89
00:05:18,333 --> 00:05:19,625
Great, let's hear it.

90
00:05:22,208 --> 00:05:23,125
It's small.

91
00:05:23,208 --> 00:05:25,125
-What?
-It's really small.

92
00:05:25,208 --> 00:05:28,958
-What's the exact number of--
-How the hell should I know?

93
00:05:29,041 --> 00:05:31,875
Civilization had Wiki[beep]ia
when you were alive right?

94
00:05:31,958 --> 00:05:33,500
What am I, huh?

95
00:05:33,583 --> 00:05:36,333
Am I Wiki[bleep]ia?
I don't think so!

96
00:05:36,416 --> 00:05:40,500
I'm your amazing manager,
The Kotaro Tatsumi!

97
00:05:40,583 --> 00:05:42,750
[TAE groans]

98
00:05:42,833 --> 00:05:44,625
I chose you specifically,

99
00:05:44,708 --> 00:05:46,583
because I knew you'd take
the world by storm

100
00:05:46,666 --> 00:05:48,250
when you became Saga's idols!

101
00:05:48,333 --> 00:05:50,500
And tomorrow, you're going
to take the first major step

102
00:05:50,583 --> 00:05:52,166
toward making that happen,
by performing in

103
00:05:52,250 --> 00:05:55,125
the Shachi-no-mon Public Concert
over at Saga Castle!

104
00:05:55,208 --> 00:05:56,833
Clearly delusional.

105
00:05:56,916 --> 00:05:58,333
Not clearly!

106
00:05:58,416 --> 00:06:00,541
You can pull it off,
just like yesterday's concert!

107
00:06:00,625 --> 00:06:03,000
Huh? I don't know
what you're talking about!

108
00:06:03,083 --> 00:06:04,750
You had the whole house jumpin'!

109
00:06:04,833 --> 00:06:08,708
-Right, Sakura?
-Uh, I guess so. Kind of. Yeah!

110
00:06:10,083 --> 00:06:11,375
[thud]

111
00:06:11,458 --> 00:06:14,583
In the meantime,
let's start today's rehearsal!

112
00:06:14,666 --> 00:06:16,625
[KOTARO]
One-and-two-and-three-and-four!

113
00:06:16,708 --> 00:06:18,458
You see how I'm doing it?

114
00:06:18,541 --> 00:06:21,916
One, two, three, four, go!

115
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,625
[SAKURA] Still can't figure out
how I got here.

116
00:06:24,708 --> 00:06:25,958
[KOTARO] You're putting
the Zs in "zombies".

117
00:06:26,041 --> 00:06:29,541
-[LILY giggles]
-[KOTARO] And good...

118
00:06:29,625 --> 00:06:33,000
-[TAE groaning]
-[JUNKO screams, whimpers]

119
00:06:33,083 --> 00:06:34,166
[KOTARO]
Keep practicing, please!

120
00:06:34,250 --> 00:06:35,791
[SAKURA]
There's no way we can

121
00:06:35,875 --> 00:06:37,500
pull this off by tomorrow.
-[KOTARO] Come on you look dead!

122
00:06:37,583 --> 00:06:40,958
[KOTARO] And good, and good, and
good, good, good, good, good.

123
00:06:41,041 --> 00:06:43,541
And good, and good, good, good.

124
00:06:43,625 --> 00:06:46,833
[SAKURA] Why's she looking
at me like that?

125
00:06:46,916 --> 00:06:49,708
[SAKURA] Oh my gosh,
these blankets are really heavy!

126
00:06:51,125 --> 00:06:52,583
[groans]

127
00:06:52,666 --> 00:06:54,666
[JUNKO whimpering]

128
00:06:56,416 --> 00:06:59,416
Sorry, I wish I knew
what you wanted from me!

129
00:07:02,083 --> 00:07:04,750
[SAKURA] Ai was an idol
before she died, right?

130
00:07:04,833 --> 00:07:07,250
She seems really familiar.

131
00:07:07,333 --> 00:07:08,250
-Hey!
-[SAKURA gasps]

132
00:07:08,333 --> 00:07:09,833
So, your name's Sakura, right?

133
00:07:09,916 --> 00:07:11,083
Um. Yes?

134
00:07:11,166 --> 00:07:12,875
What school?

135
00:07:12,958 --> 00:07:15,458
Dumbass. What middle
school'd you go to?

136
00:07:15,541 --> 00:07:19,958
Oh. Okay... sorry,
but, uh, I don't remember.

137
00:07:20,041 --> 00:07:21,333
♪

138
00:07:21,416 --> 00:07:22,708
Screw with me
and I'll make you double-dead.

139
00:07:22,791 --> 00:07:24,291
Oh no, I would
never screw with you.

140
00:07:24,375 --> 00:07:26,583
I really don't remember anything
from when I was alive--

141
00:07:26,666 --> 00:07:29,208
Yeah, yeah, well you better
make yourself remember and fast,

142
00:07:29,291 --> 00:07:31,250
-got it punk?
-[SAKURA whimpers]

143
00:07:32,541 --> 00:07:35,125
Why the hell are you
buyin' into this idol crap?

144
00:07:35,208 --> 00:07:36,833
Goody-two-shoes.

145
00:07:36,916 --> 00:07:38,708
Want me to kick your ass?

146
00:07:38,791 --> 00:07:40,750
What? No, not at all.

147
00:07:40,833 --> 00:07:42,958
It's just...
the show's tomorrow.

148
00:07:43,041 --> 00:07:45,458
So, let's have a rally.

149
00:07:45,541 --> 00:07:46,416
[gasps]

150
00:07:47,833 --> 00:07:49,625
Like this!

151
00:07:49,708 --> 00:07:51,083
[whimpers]

152
00:07:51,166 --> 00:07:54,416
Man, this zombie thing
friggin' sucks.

153
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:57,083
I bet my Tamagotchi's
way past dead now.

154
00:07:59,083 --> 00:08:01,958
[whimpers, exhales with relief]

155
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,625
Wow, she's scary.

156
00:08:07,916 --> 00:08:09,083
Huh?

157
00:08:11,125 --> 00:08:12,958
[SAKURA] Wait a second.
Where'd Ai go?

158
00:08:24,791 --> 00:08:27,000
[wakes up, pants]

159
00:08:27,083 --> 00:08:28,583
-[ROMERO growls]
-Zombie dog?

160
00:08:28,666 --> 00:08:30,791
[growling, smashing
against the door]

161
00:08:30,875 --> 00:08:33,750
-[gasps]
-[fast footsteps]

162
00:08:33,833 --> 00:08:37,916
[yapping]

163
00:08:50,083 --> 00:08:52,083
This place is a madhouse!

164
00:08:52,166 --> 00:08:53,333
[door opens]

165
00:08:53,416 --> 00:08:54,541
-[SAKURA] Ai?
-[AI gasps]

166
00:08:54,625 --> 00:08:56,916
[SAKURA] Hello? You there?

167
00:09:01,916 --> 00:09:03,625
[BOTH scream]

168
00:09:06,416 --> 00:09:07,625
Found you!

169
00:09:07,708 --> 00:09:09,208
Oh, hey, Junko's here too?

170
00:09:09,291 --> 00:09:12,000
What are you guys doing?

171
00:09:13,541 --> 00:09:15,500
-Leaving, obviously.
-I'm leaving.

172
00:09:15,583 --> 00:09:17,583
-Huh?
-[AI] This is ridiculous!

173
00:09:17,666 --> 00:09:20,500
There's no reason I should have
to stay and put up with it!

174
00:09:20,583 --> 00:09:22,583
[SAKURA]
Please, you can't go out there!

175
00:09:22,666 --> 00:09:24,000
It's not safe!

176
00:09:24,083 --> 00:09:26,250
You're still worried
about that video?

177
00:09:26,333 --> 00:09:27,583
Nothing like
that's gonna happen.

178
00:09:27,666 --> 00:09:30,083
But I got shot by a policeman!

179
00:09:30,166 --> 00:09:32,083
Let's go.
That Tae girl scares me.

180
00:09:32,166 --> 00:09:34,916
She doesn't say anything,
just bites.

181
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:38,083
I mean yeah, that'll take some
getting used to, but it's fine!

182
00:09:38,166 --> 00:09:40,416
-[AI grunts]
-Ai! Get down!

183
00:09:40,500 --> 00:09:42,916
-Let me go!
-Come back!

184
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,458
[arms snap]

185
00:09:45,416 --> 00:09:46,750
[BOTH grunt]

186
00:09:48,083 --> 00:09:49,666
[JUNKO gasps]

187
00:09:53,208 --> 00:09:54,833
[SAKURA]
Guys, this is dangerous.

188
00:09:54,916 --> 00:09:56,041
We shouldn't be here.

189
00:09:56,125 --> 00:09:57,333
[AI] Keep quiet.

190
00:09:57,416 --> 00:09:59,666
[JUNKO] Um, can I ask
where we're going?

191
00:09:59,750 --> 00:10:00,708
[AI] Tokyo.

192
00:10:00,791 --> 00:10:02,125
Not Tokyo!

193
00:10:02,208 --> 00:10:03,750
We don't have any money!

194
00:10:03,833 --> 00:10:06,250
They'll blow us up!
You saw the clips!

195
00:10:06,333 --> 00:10:07,708
Hey, don't remind me!

196
00:10:07,791 --> 00:10:10,291
[SAKURA] Or maybe they'll
just beat us up real bad!

197
00:10:10,375 --> 00:10:13,833
[AI] You can
go back if you want.

198
00:10:16,041 --> 00:10:17,458
Please don't do this.

199
00:10:17,541 --> 00:10:20,625
You really think a bunch
of zombies can be idols?

200
00:10:20,708 --> 00:10:23,625
You jumped on board
with that way too easily.

201
00:10:23,708 --> 00:10:26,375
[AI]
Are you stupid or something?

202
00:10:26,458 --> 00:10:28,333
[SAKURA]
I guess I might be.

203
00:10:28,416 --> 00:10:31,708
Maybe I didn't take time
to think it through.

204
00:10:31,791 --> 00:10:33,125
Still though.

205
00:10:33,208 --> 00:10:35,875
[SAKUA] When all of us
were on stage together.

206
00:10:35,958 --> 00:10:38,000
I got this strange feeling,

207
00:10:38,083 --> 00:10:40,625
like my heart was buzzing
or something.

208
00:10:40,708 --> 00:10:43,000
It made me so happy.

209
00:10:43,083 --> 00:10:45,916
I may not remember anything from
before I was a zombie,

210
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,250
but I know that I
felt something

211
00:10:47,333 --> 00:10:48,708
similar to that when
I was alive.

212
00:10:48,791 --> 00:10:51,625
So I want to have
that feeling again.

213
00:10:51,708 --> 00:10:53,375
I want to know what it is.

214
00:10:53,458 --> 00:10:57,625
That's the reason I'm so eager
to get back on stage.

215
00:10:57,708 --> 00:11:00,250
[music plays in the distance]

216
00:11:00,333 --> 00:11:03,208
-[car approaches]
-[music stops]

217
00:11:03,291 --> 00:11:05,083
-[car door closes]
-[footsteps]

218
00:11:05,166 --> 00:11:07,000
-[RAPPER 1 beatboxing]
-[RAPPER 2] Yo!

219
00:11:07,083 --> 00:11:09,000
Yo! Yo! Yo! Yo!

220
00:11:09,083 --> 00:11:10,375
[RAPPER 3] Check check check!

221
00:11:10,458 --> 00:11:12,500
Oh no, what are
those scary guys doing?

222
00:11:12,583 --> 00:11:14,083
They're rapping... weird.

223
00:11:14,166 --> 00:11:15,666
Mic check. Yo!

224
00:11:27,208 --> 00:11:28,875
Yo, yo, yo!

225
00:11:33,958 --> 00:11:36,541
Oh my God, they're coming
right towards us!

226
00:11:36,625 --> 00:11:38,875
Let's just walk away
and don't make eye contact.

227
00:11:45,833 --> 00:11:48,916
[AI gasps]

228
00:11:51,916 --> 00:11:55,333
[RAPPER 1 continues beatboxing]

229
00:11:55,416 --> 00:11:57,041
-[RAPPER 3] Check check one-two!
-[RAPPER 2] Yo!

230
00:11:57,125 --> 00:11:59,125
[MALE COP] Well, lookie here,
what I just found.

231
00:11:59,208 --> 00:12:01,625
You kids wanna tell me
why you're creepin' around?

232
00:12:01,708 --> 00:12:03,041
[SAKURA]
Is that?

233
00:12:03,125 --> 00:12:04,208
Aw, man!

234
00:12:04,291 --> 00:12:06,416
Come on, we didn't
even do anything!

235
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:08,750
Harassin' girls
is an epic fail.

236
00:12:08,833 --> 00:12:11,750
Leave 'em alone,
or it's straight to jail, boy!

237
00:12:11,833 --> 00:12:13,916
-Oh, good. Please help us, sir!
-Ai!

238
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,541
[SAKURA]
Stay back!

239
00:12:15,625 --> 00:12:17,208
[whimpers]

240
00:12:17,291 --> 00:12:18,958
Help us.

241
00:12:19,041 --> 00:12:20,625
♪

242
00:12:20,708 --> 00:12:22,541
-[MALE COP] Not again!
-[RAPPER 2] Hold up!

243
00:12:22,625 --> 00:12:23,541
This ain't happenin'.

244
00:12:23,625 --> 00:12:24,791
[RAPPER 3]
They look dead!

245
00:12:24,875 --> 00:12:25,791
We should run now!

246
00:12:25,875 --> 00:12:27,416
-[gunshot]
-[glass shatters]

247
00:12:27,500 --> 00:12:30,125
[whimpering]

248
00:12:32,125 --> 00:12:34,041
[glass falls]

249
