This ain't happenin'!

266
00:13:19,208 --> 00:13:21,041
[KOTARO]
From the top, now.

267
00:13:23,666 --> 00:13:25,708
We're gonna have to be
careful out there tomorrow.

268
00:13:25,791 --> 00:13:26,791
-Hey!
-[gasps]

269
00:13:26,875 --> 00:13:28,541
[SAKI chewing]

270
00:13:28,625 --> 00:13:29,750
[grunts]

271
00:13:29,833 --> 00:13:31,000
You wanna die?

272
00:13:31,083 --> 00:13:33,541
-Ah, sorry! I'll leave!
-[SAKI] Hold it!

273
00:13:33,625 --> 00:13:34,708
Eh...

274
00:13:36,166 --> 00:13:39,000
Why do you do everything
that jackass with the sunglasses

275
