285
00:14:01,666 --> 00:14:03,875
-couldn't you try to--
-Nah, screw that! Damn.

286
00:14:03,958 --> 00:14:06,750
Do I have to spell it out
for you, or what?

287
00:14:08,666 --> 00:14:12,083
[footsteps]

288
00:14:15,625 --> 00:14:17,958
[KOTARO] It's not about
technique, it's about heart!

289
00:14:18,041 --> 00:14:19,666
Trust me, kid.

290
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:22,791
Make up is the paintbrush
that colors the whole world.

291
00:14:22,875 --> 00:14:24,083
It's in your hands!

292
00:14:24,166 --> 00:14:27,541
