understand any of that.

293
00:14:27,625 --> 00:14:30,250
Hot damn!
This might really work!

294
00:14:30,333 --> 00:14:33,958
-Oh, wow! Pretty!
-That's so kind of you.

295
00:14:34,041 --> 00:14:36,541
You look quite radiant
yourself, Lady Lily.

296
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:41,125
[SAKURA] Hope this turns
out okay.

297
00:14:41,208 --> 00:14:43,583
[STAFF 1]
Yes, right this way, ma'am.

298
00:14:43,666 --> 00:14:45,625
I dunno, man. This doesn't
seem like the kinda place

299
00:14:45,708 --> 00:14:47,333
you can rock out at.

300
00:14:47,416 --> 00:14:48,958
Just some ol' codgers, innit.

301
00:14:49,041 --> 00:14:51,666
[SAKURA] Remember,
don't give away our secret.

302
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:53,875
You mean the zombie thing?

303
00:14:53,958 --> 00:14:55,875
No worries,
that'll be super easy!

304
00:14:55,958 --> 00:14:57,500
-We're alive!
-[MEN AND GIRLS] Hm?

305
00:14:57,583 --> 00:14:59,333
Ssh, Saki!

306
00:14:59,416 --> 00:15:00,750
Know what else?

307
00:15:00,833 --> 00:15:03,625
In this getup.
I'm freakin' sexy!

308
00:15:03,708 --> 00:15:06,333
-Okay, okay!
-[STAFF 2] Sorry for the wait.

309
00:15:06,416 --> 00:15:08,041
Let's see.

310
00:15:08,125 --> 00:15:09,916
