312
00:15:11,416 --> 00:15:14,291
Ah, actually sir,
our group's called Death Musume.

313
00:15:14,375 --> 00:15:17,583
[KOTARO] Starting today,
you're called Green Face!

314
00:15:20,166 --> 00:15:22,000
-Mr. Kotaro--
-Listen!

315
00:15:22,083 --> 00:15:24,083
You get out there
and show these people

316
00:15:24,166 --> 00:15:26,291
