317
00:15:26,375 --> 00:15:30,708
-But what does that mean?
-Okay! Go now! Go, go, go!

318
00:15:35,250 --> 00:15:37,583
[TAE groans]

319
00:15:37,666 --> 00:15:39,208
Uh...

320
00:15:39,291 --> 00:15:41,125
Um. Hello there!

321
00:15:41,208 --> 00:15:43,291
We are, uh, Green Musume.

322
00:15:43,375 --> 00:15:45,041
No wait, I mean Green Face!

323
00:15:45,125 --> 00:15:48,125
Are they on some kinda
"save the environment" kick now?

324
00:15:48,208 --> 00:15:50,916
Oi, are you ladies
not doin' death metal anymore?

325
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:53,416
Anyway, you can
call me Number One,

326
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:55,583
and my friend here
is Number Zero.

327
00:15:55,666 --> 00:15:57,083
Then, to my left,

328
00:15:57,166 --> 00:16:00,583
Numbers Two,
and Three, Number Four.

329
00:16:00,666 --> 00:16:04,250
Oh, Number Five!
And that's Number Six!

330
00:16:04,333 --> 00:16:06,375
We're a brand-new idol group.

331
00:16:06,458 --> 00:16:09,083
And our mission is to revive
Saga using our music!

332
00:16:09,166 --> 00:16:11,458
Our skills are kind
of green, too,

333
00:16:11,541 --> 00:16:13,416
but we've practiced really hard!

334
00:16:15,291 --> 00:16:17,291
-[TAE groans]
-Well, let's do this!

335
00:16:17,375 --> 00:16:19,541
[SAKURA]
Go!

336
00:16:19,625 --> 00:16:22,500
-[TAE groans]
-Uh...

337
00:16:22,583 --> 00:16:24,833
Music, come on!

338
00:16:24,916 --> 00:16:28,875
♪

339
