352
00:17:26,791 --> 00:17:31,750
-[imitating chewing]
-Wanna bite?

353
00:17:35,250 --> 00:17:39,125
Um. Ta-da! It's a trick!

354
00:17:39,208 --> 00:17:42,458
I have superpowers!

355
00:17:42,541 --> 00:17:46,916
Ahh! Hey, Saki, heads up!

356
00:17:50,458 --> 00:17:51,250
[grunts]

357
00:17:51,333 --> 00:17:53,875
Does that not even hurt?

358
00:17:53,958 --> 00:17:57,625
Ta-da!
It's another trick.

359
00:17:57,708 --> 00:17:58,833
Woo!

360
00:17:58,916 --> 00:18:01,083
-Undead Magic!
-[AUDIENCE applause]

361
00:18:01,166 --> 00:18:03,458
